| S0   | Spring | Fall   | 20     | 0+20   | March 21     | Northward Equinox  |
| S1   | Summer | Winter | 110    | 3+18   | June 19      | Northward Solstice |
| S2   | Fall   | Spring | 205    | 6+21   | September 22 | Southward Equinox  |
