|---------|----------|----------|-------|
| .30:.48 | .30\>.18 | .48\<.18 | work0 |
| .48:.52 | .48\>.04 | .52\<.04 | lunch |
| .52:.70 | .52\>.18 | .70\<.18 | work1 |

